description:
Anyone who claims AOC should become the face of the Democratic party learned nothing from the 2024 election. However, we can only hope that the DNC jumps on this bandwagon, as it does them no favors while landing Republicans more wins than the left could have ever imagined.

Jamaal Bowman claimed that the problem with the Democratic party is not that they have gone completely insane, but that they just need a new face. Mike Lawler, who has hinted he wants to run for the Gov. of New York, responded by claiming this will "mobilize voters way more than Nancy Pelosi ever did."
